oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Family history page from a Bible carried by Sgt. Julius B. Luckenbach, Co. I, 33rd Ind. Inf. Regt., USA
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This family history page comes from a Bible carried during the Civil War by Sgt. Julius B. Luckenbach, Co. I, 33rd Indiana. Inf. Regt., USA. The Bible dates to the Civil War era and originally belonged to his brother George.
